high_descs: Turn left and go to the black trash can in the right corner.
Pick up the pencil in the trash can.
Turn around and go to the left side of the dining table.
Place the pencil in the bowl towards the corner.
Pick up and bowl with the pencil in it.
Go around the table and go into the living room and to the left side of the coffee table.
Place the bowl with the pencil in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pencil in the bowl on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the black wastebasket in the corner to your right.
Take the pencil out of the wastebasket.
Turn right and go to the nearest corner of the dining table.
Put the pencil into the bowl nearest that corner.
Pick up the bowl with the pencil in it.
Go around the left side of the table and sofa, to the coffee table that is in front of the sofa.
Put the bowl on top of the coffee table on the side closer to the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl holding a pencil onto a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the door, then turn right and walk up to the black bin.
Pick up the pencil out of the black bin.
Turn around and walk around the small table to the large glass dining table.
Put the pencil in the grey bowl that is on the closest corner of the glass dining table.
Pick up the grey bowl with the pencil in it off of the glass table.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the grey bowl with the pencil in it on top of the glass coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey bowl with a pencil in it on the coffee table.
